               <msContents>
                  <summary>A holograph copy of the first volume of ʻAlī Ibrāhīm Khān's anthology of
                     masnavi poetry, . <title type="main">Khulāṣat al-kalām</title>.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_318-item1">
                     <author key="person_20524990" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/20524990"
                        change="#ids-cleanup">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard" role="ann aut scr"
                           change="#role-assignment">ʻAlī Ibrāhīm Khān, d. 1793 or 4</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" role="ann aut scr" change="#role-assignment">نوّاب
                           أمين الدولة عزيز الملك علي إبراهيم خان بهادر نصير جنگ</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt" role="ann aut scr"
                           change="#role-assignment">Khayāl</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" type="alt" role="ann aut scr"
                           change="#role-assignment">خیال</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_6060">Khulāṣat al-kalām</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_6060">خلاصة الكلام</title>
                     <note>The first half of the work from the letter الف to the first page of
                        letter صاد.</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa">تعالی الله ما قصیر فهما کوتاه بیان را چه یارا که زبان
                        حمد و ثنا متکلم بی زبان توانیم گشود</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa">مکین دان فیروزه آسمان</explicit>
                     <listBibl>
                        <bibl>Ethé 390</bibl>
                        <bibl>
                           <title level="a">"On the earliest Persian Biography of Poets, by Muhammad
                              Aúfi, and on some other Works of the class called Tazkirat ul
                              Shuârá"</title>
                           <author key="person_20108923" role="oth"
                              change="#role-assignment #ids-cleanup">
                              <name>N. Bland</name>
                           </author>
                           <title level="j">Journal of the Royal Asiatic Society of Great Britain
                              and Ireland, vol. ix</title>
                           <biblScope>158ff.</biblScope>
                           <date calendar="#Gregorian">1848</date>
                        </bibl>
                     </listBibl>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>While Bland and Elliott report ʻAlī Ibrāhīm Khān's takhalluṣ as "Khalīl",
                        it is given here as "Khayāl".</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
