                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item>
                           <label>Marginalia</label> Infrequent marginalia in the hand of the
                           copyist/compiler, <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard"
                              key="person_20524990" role="ann aut scr"
                              change="#role-assignment #ids-cleanup">ʻAlī Ibrāhīm Khān, d. 1793 or
